e: ￹`Caay~ `ka~ `sa'osi~ `cingra~ `a~ `mi~`lhakelong~ `i~ `titaanan~.￺He was not included in the count to go with us.￻沒有把他算在我們行列之中
￹`Sa~`'osi~`en~ `ko~ `ma~`tahidang~`ay~.￺Count how many have been invited￻請點清被邀請的人
￹`Sa~`'osi~`en~ / `asip~`en~ / `'osi~`en~ `konini~ `a~ `tilid~.￺Read this writing.￻請你讀一下這一篇文章 (一本書或一封信)
